[Brief summary paragraph]

## Key Points
- [Point 1]
- [Point 2]

## Action Items (if any)
- [Action item]

NOTE TO SUMMARIZE:
${text}

SUMMARY:`;

    try {
      const response = await fetch(this.baseUrl, {
        method: 'POST',
        headers: {
          'Content-Type': 'application/json',
          'x-api-key': this.apiKey,
          'anthropic-version': '2023-06-01',
          'anthropic-dangerous-direct-password-access': 'true'
